description: This All in one Universal Adapter Plug with 2.1A Dual USB Port allows you to plug your small appliance or computer into outlets around the world while charging your phone, ipad or tablets via the USB port.Has a LED charging indicator.Built in surge protector. Accommodates grounded and ungrounded plugs.This adaptor plug modifies electrical outlet, does not change the voltage. Supports universal voltage 125V-250V.Works in worldwide: United States, Canada, Europe, Middle East, South America, Asia, The Caribbean, Great Britain ,Ireland, Africa, Hong Kong, Singapore, Australia, Fiji, New Zealand, China, Japan, and more than 150 countries
title: Yubi Power Universal World Wide Travel Plug Charger with 2.1A Dual USB Adaptor,White
